&lt;h3&gt;Role:&amp;nbsp;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p&gt;We are seeking a highly experienced Site Reliability Engineer located in Europe, with a strong track record of tackling complex reliability and scalability challenges, and a history of providing technical guidance to teams. If you&#39;re a seasoned problem-solver with a passion for automation and operational excellence, and enjoy elevating the skills of those around you, we want to hear from you.&lt;/p&gt;
